ml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:375:\"<p>Dear loyal customers, Today we are announcing the updates of all our themes, plugins, and...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/changes-in-themebeez-com-and-migration-to-creamcode-org/\">Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog\">Themebeez Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Themebeez editor\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8920:\"\n<p>Dear loyal customers,</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Today we are announcing the updates of all our themes, plugins, and license manager update.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We have had issues with our old license manager. We have left it for good and moved to a new license manager. So, for us it had been hectic previous couple of days.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We did our best to provide you all the updates of new versions premium themes and plugins that support the new license manager. But at the end, our old license manager that should be working correctly somehow broke. So, we could not provide you all the updates of new versions premium themes and plugins as before. We are truly sorry for it and we apologize for the inconvenience caused you due to it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can still download the updated new version of premium theme or plugin from <a href=\"https://creamcode.org/login/\" class=\"rank-math-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">your account</a>. But to update the theme or plugin to new versions, it needs to be done manually.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Download latest version of theme or plugin</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Please, follow the instructions below to download the new versions of premium themes and plugins:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Log into <a href=\"https://creamcode.org/login/\" class=\"rank-math-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Your Account</a>. After successful login, you&#8217;ll be prompted to your account dashboard.</li><li>Under Downloads tab, you&#8217;ll find your purchased theme or plugin and download button to download them. Click on the download button to download the theme or plugin file.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"622\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-download-file-1024x622.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10155\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-download-file-1024x622.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-download-file-300x182.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-download-file-768x466.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-download-file.png 1461w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org 1\"><figcaption>Example: download button to download Fascinate pro theme.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Update the theme or plugin to latest version</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Once the download of theme or plugin file is complete. Follow the instructions below to update the theme or plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"532\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/overwrite-exisiting-theme-wp-dashboard-1024x532.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10158\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/overwrite-exisiting-theme-wp-dashboard-1024x532.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/overwrite-exisiting-theme-wp-dashboard-300x156.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/overwrite-exisiting-theme-wp-dashboard-768x399.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/overwrite-exisiting-theme-wp-dashboard.png 1376w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org 2\"><figcaption>Example: Overwrite theme/Pugin file</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Log into your website&#8217;s dashboard.</li><li>If you are updating a theme, then click on <strong>Appearance &gt; Themes</strong>. If you are updating a plugin, then click on <strong>Plugins</strong>.</li><li>Click the Add New button and then click on Upload Theme or Upload Plugin button.</li><li>Upload the downloaded theme or plugin file(.zip) and click on Install Now button.</li><li>Click on the Replace current with an <strong>uploaded</strong> button to update the theme or plugin. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>FYI:</strong> Since Orchid store pro is a plugin you need to upload plugin via Dashboard &gt; Plugin &gt; Add new.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> You must have WordPress version 5.5 or greater to update following above instructions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have older versions WordPress than 5.5, please use <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/article/ftp-clients/\" class=\"rank-math-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FTP client</a> to update your theme or plugin via FTP protocol.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Extract the files the the downloaded the theme or plugin contains. You should have a folder named as theme or plugin itself, containing theme or plugin files.</li><li>Using an <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/getting-started/ftp-clients/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FTP cli</a><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/article/ftp-clients/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">e</a><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/getting-started/ftp-clients/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">nt</a> to access your host web server. Navigate to <strong>/wp-content/themes/</strong> directory to upload theme files or navigate to <strong>/wp-content/plugins/</strong> directory to upload plugin files.</li><li>Upload the theme or plugin folder to respective directory on your host server.</li><li>This will update your theme or plugin on your server.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Get and update your new license</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>After you have successfully updated your theme or plugin, on your website&#8217;s dashboard, click on the <strong>License Manager</strong> and you&#8217;ll see that your license field empty.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Follow the instructions below to get and update your new license.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"607\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-licence-key-1024x607.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10157\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-licence-key-1024x607.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-licence-key-300x178.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-licence-key-768x456.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/creamcode-licence-key.png 1369w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org 3\"><figcaption>Example: Click the red key icon</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Log into <a href=\"https://creamcode.org/login/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Your Account</a>. After successful login, you&#8217;ll be prompted to your account dashboard.</li><li>Navigate to the License tab. Click on the key icon associated with your theme or plugin. The license key will be displayed. Copy the license key.</li><li>Back to your website&#8217;s dashboard, click on License Manager and then paste the license key. Then click on the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button.</li><li>Once the license key is saved. Click on the <strong>Activate License</strong> button. This will activate the license for the theme or plugin.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"283\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/activate-new-licence-key-wp-dashboard-1024x283.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10159\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/activate-new-licence-key-wp-dashboard-1024x283.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/activate-new-licence-key-wp-dashboard-300x83.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/activate-new-licence-key-wp-dashboard-768x213.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/activate-new-licence-key-wp-dashboard-1536x425.png 1536w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/activate-new-licence-key-wp-dashboard.png 1651w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org 4\"><figcaption>Example: New license key manager</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We know this is a kind of hassle to go through all these processes. We truly apologize for this. We hope you&#8217;ll understand and patiently update your theme or plugin and activate the new license.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If any issues occur during the download, update, and license activation process of your theme or plugin, then please contact us from <a aria-label=\"our support page (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"rank-math-link\">our support page</a>. We&#8217;ll assist you and provide support to you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wish you Happy New Year 2021 ✨🎉🎈. Have a great time. Have a great holiday.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best wishes,</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cream Code Family</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/changes-in-themebeez-com-and-migration-to-creamcode-org/\">Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollo