ownloads WP Security Audit Log</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Anti-Malware Security and Brute-Force Firewall</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"475\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Anti-Malware-Security-and-Brute-Force-Firewall-Screen_Shot-1024x475.png\" alt=\"Anti-Malware Security and Brute-Force Firewall Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7881\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Anti-Malware-Security-and-Brute-Force-Firewall-Screen_Shot-1024x475.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Anti-Malware-Security-and-Brute-Force-Firewall-Screen_Shot-300x139.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Anti-Malware-Security-and-Brute-Force-Firewall-Screen_Shot-768x356.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Anti-Malware-Security-and-Brute-Force-Firewall-Screen_Shot.png 1252w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org 130\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Anti-Malware Security and Brute-Force Firewall Plugin is a great WordPress security plugin that is easy to setup. This plugin stops the malware to infect the website and also stops brute force attacks. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin is available in both free and premium versions. The free version of this plugin has basic features, whereas the premium version has updated features. Checking the integrity of WordPress files and patching wp-login falls under the premium features of this plugin. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Automatically removes backdoor scripts, security threats, and database injections</li><li>Prevents DDoS and brute force attacks by patching login</li><li>Powerful firewall</li><li>Comprehensive Website scanner</li><li>Prevents other plugins with known vulnerabilities</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gotmls/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads Anti-Malware Security</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Really Simple SSL</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"481\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Really-Simple-SSL-Screen_Shot-1024x481.png\" alt=\"Really Simple SSL Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7882\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Really-Simple-SSL-Screen_Shot-1024x481.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Really-Simple-SSL-Screen_Shot-300x141.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Really-Simple-SSL-Screen_Shot-768x361.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Really-Simple-SSL-Screen_Shot.png 1246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"Changes in Themebeez.com and Migration to CreamCode.Org 131\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Rally Simple SSL is one of the best WordPress Security Plugins, which helps you to automatically detect and configure your website to run over the https. With this plugin, the site will move to SSL. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin is available in packages of premium versions, which includes an unlimited package of $159, a professional package of $59, and a personal package of $29 for a yearly plan. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Premium email support </li><li>Mixed content fixer in the back-end </li><li>Enables HTTP Script Transport Security </li><li>Detection of source of mixed content </li><li>Easy implementable security headers</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/really-simple-ssl/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads Really Simple SSL</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the right and affordable security plugin for your website is essential as you need to be aware of certain malware and attacks. Hence, you need to be very careful and choose a free or a premium plan as per your website. If you want to make your website free from any kind of attack, you should certainly choose a premium plan. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, you can choose any among the listed WordPress security plugins to secure your website. Go through the features of all the plugins listed and choose according to the demand of your website. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-security-plugins/\">13+ Best WordPress Security Plugins</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog\">Themebeez Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-security-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Ato